WEBVTT

00:01.978 --> 00:04.423
Pull the rabbit out of your hat.

00:04.423 --> 00:09.234
That's the secret of both
trial law and life.

00:09.234 --> 00:11.375
Rabbits… –Yeah.

00:11.375 --> 00:12.744
Christine Polley…

00:12.744 --> 00:14.178
Ex­girlfriend tried to kill me.

00:14.178 --> 00:15.497
She tried to kill you.

00:15.497 --> 00:17.087
–She did.
–And now she wants out.

00:17.087 --> 00:18.643
She does. –Alan.

00:18.643 --> 00:21.128
She's stalking you.
She tried to kill you,

00:21.128 --> 00:22.900
she was institutionalized,
now she's out,

00:22.900 --> 00:24.031
and she's stalking you.

00:24.031 --> 00:26.423
Freedom is a privilege, 
Mr Shore, not a right.

00:26.423 --> 00:28.497
–A privilege. 
–Yes, and it's revocable,

00:28.497 --> 00:31.688
especially if you try to run
someone over with an automobile.

00:31.688 --> 00:33.305
I got my old job back.

00:33.305 --> 00:37.243
It's truly fantastic news, 
isn't it? Alan?

00:37.243 --> 00:38.675
