02:44.066 --> 02:45.837
Denny, we've got…

02:46.984 --> 02:47.809
What's going on?

02:47.809 --> 02:49.381
A little maintenance work, Paul.

02:49.381 --> 02:51.707
Wouldn't hurt you, by the way.
You look like a prune.

02:51.707 --> 02:53.861
We have the Kaneb meeting
in 15 minutes.

02:53.861 --> 02:55.495
Excellent. Why do I care?

02:55.495 --> 02:58.126
You care because this is
the construction project

02:58.126 --> 03:01.193
that the entire firm has been
working on for 18 months.

03:01.193 --> 03:03.599
You care because Byron Kaneb cares,

03:03.599 --> 03:06.109
and he expects you to be present.

03:06.842 --> 03:08.347
Damn it, man, what have you done?

03:08.347 --> 03:10.466
The needle broke.

03:10.872 --> 03:12.259
Not to worry, just 
let me remove it.

03:12.259 --> 03:13.528
Don't you touch me.

03:13.528 --> 03:15.377
Mr Crane, half the needle
is still in your forehead.

03:15.377 --> 03:17.871
–Just let me remove..
–You're not touching me!

03:17.871 --> 03:19.706
Get Dr Michaels back down here.

03:19.706 --> 03:23.361
This is what happens when I let 
his kids cut their teeth on my head.

03:23.361 --> 03:25.846
If I could just remove
the needle… –Don't you touch me!

03:25.846 --> 03:28.406
Denny, there's a needle
in your head.

03:28.406 --> 03:30.010
Let him at least remove it.

03:30.010 --> 03:32.977
Get me Dr Michaels!

03:35.701 --> 03:37.868
I really don't need
a second chair for this.

03:37.868 --> 03:40.085
Sexual harassment is 
a specialty of mine.

03:40.085 --> 03:42.386
Mine, too. –No doubt, 
but while your experience

03:42.386 --> 03:44.490
tends to be more hands­on, mine…

03:44.490 --> 03:46.379
tends to be more wishful thinking.

03:46.379 --> 03:49.205
Not to mention, you ooze.

03:49.205 --> 03:50.736
I ooze?

03:50.736 --> 03:54.894
Yes, that certain something that 
subliminally champions misogyny.

03:54.894 --> 03:56.756
You need me.

03:59.042 --> 04:00.515
Lori,

04:01.176 --> 04:06.839
as much as I may want you,
desire you, even,

04:06.839 --> 04:09.275
I do not need you.

04:09.275 --> 04:11.221
See that right there?

04:11.221 --> 04:12.771
Ooze!

04:16.790 --> 04:18.663
When can I dig my hole?

04:18.663 --> 04:20.261
We're almost there, Byron.

04:20.261 --> 04:22.693
Don't tell me we're 
almost there, Paul.

04:22.693 --> 04:25.484
We've been almost there
for six months.

04:25.484 --> 04:27.020
When will we be there?

04:27.020 --> 04:30.260
City council agreed to the variance
for the golf course on Monday.

04:30.260 --> 04:31.417
Now today we're expecting an answer

04:31.417 --> 04:33.341
from the redevelopment commission
for the outdoor mall,

04:33.341 --> 04:35.250
and my sources say they're 
gonna rule in our favor.

04:35.250 --> 04:36.684
What about the damn E.P.A.?

04:36.684 --> 04:38.773
The blue spotted salamander 
just got downgraded

04:38.773 --> 04:41.072
from endangered to 
threatened last week,

04:41.072 --> 04:43.222
so the marina looks 
like a go except for…

04:43.222 --> 04:44.353
Except for what?

04:44.353 --> 04:48.567
It seems there's a river
where some salmon spawn.

04:48.567 --> 04:52.867
Evidently, there's some environmental
lawyer who's making a stink.

04:52.867 --> 04:55.326
When you say stink…

04:55.326 --> 04:58.350
He got a T.R.O.

04:59.216 --> 05:00.742
A fish?

05:00.742 --> 05:03.737
My city's being held up by a fish?

05:03.737 --> 05:05.376
We are meeting the lawyer today.

05:05.376 --> 05:08.038
We will make it go away.

05:15.420 --> 05:18.710
Do you plan to contribute, or are you
simply assigned to mop up the ooze?

05:18.710 --> 05:19.800
Alan.

05:24.153 --> 05:25.262
Hello.

05:25.606 --> 05:27.479
Christine Pauley.

05:27.792 --> 05:29.405
Oh, I've heard so much about you.

05:29.405 --> 05:30.522
How are you?

05:30.522 --> 05:32.584
Fine, thank you.

05:33.030 --> 05:35.514
If you'll excuse us,
we're due in court. –Yes, I know.

05:35.514 --> 05:38.268
I'm opposing counsel.

05:38.493 --> 05:40.220
I beg your pardon?

05:40.220 --> 05:41.213
What do you expect me to do?

05:41.213 --> 05:43.962
I expect you to disqualify her.
This is tantamount to stalking.

05:43.962 --> 05:46.860
She got herself assigned
to this case because I'm on it.

05:46.860 --> 05:48.523
Not to mention,
as an officer of the court,

05:48.523 --> 05:51.269
I question whether Ms Pauley even
has the capacity to try a case.

05:51.269 --> 05:53.712
She was released from
a mental facility last week.

05:53.712 --> 05:55.733
Certainly, counsel,
if you wanna conflict out…

05:55.733 --> 05:56.988
I can't conflict out.

05:56.988 --> 05:58.806
I'm the only one
who knows the case here.

05:58.806 --> 06:00.830
–Ms Colson was simply put on…
–Ms Pauley,

06:00.830 --> 06:02.170
what's going on?

06:02.170 --> 06:04.171
Of all the cases to start off with,

06:04.171 --> 06:06.429
you pick one against an ex­boyfriend
you tried to kill?

06:06.429 --> 06:08.344
Actually, your honor,
I didn't pick it.

06:08.344 --> 06:09.910
–My firm came to me.
–Please, Christine…

06:09.910 --> 06:12.195
because I used to date Mr Shore,

06:12.195 --> 06:13.685
they thought I could shed some light

06:13.685 --> 06:16.276
on some of his procedural 
eccentricities, which I did.

06:16.276 --> 06:17.900
Since I also happen to have extensive

06:17.900 --> 06:19.640
experience in sexual harassment law,

06:19.640 --> 06:23.269
the senior parers asked me if 
I would first chair, I agreed.

06:23.269 --> 06:25.272
–We start at 11 A.M.
–Your honor…

06:25.272 --> 06:28.813
Mr Shore, if you wanna
conflict out, do so.

06:28.813 --> 06:33.670
But I have no legal basis
to disqualify Ms Pauley.

06:37.389 --> 06:39.084
May I speak with you alone, Alan?

06:39.084 --> 06:40.358
No, you may not, Christine.

06:40.358 --> 06:42.185
And if you choose to be 
on this case,

06:42.185 --> 06:45.376
please conduct yourself
at arm's length and on the record.

06:45.376 --> 06:47.732
It's just coincidence to you
your first case out of the hospital.

06:47.732 --> 06:49.475
I consider it a preposterous 
coincidence,

06:49.475 --> 06:50.561
you have no business trying a case.

06:50.561 --> 06:52.814
–But truth be told, the partners think—
–I know you better than your partners.

06:52.814 --> 06:55.072
How sad, you can't
be happy for me. –I'm not happy.

06:55.072 --> 06:57.447
Clearly.

07:00.001 --> 07:03.432
Well, that seemed perfectly normal.

07:05.246 --> 07:06.941
The D.A. offered three months 
suspended.

07:06.941 --> 07:08.554
I think we should take it.

07:08.554 --> 07:09.956
Does it go on my record?

07:09.956 --> 07:11.666
–Well, yes.
–The answer's no.

07:11.666 --> 07:12.905
Ramone… –I didn't do it.

07:12.905 --> 07:13.679
I didn't take that wallet.

07:13.679 --> 07:16.046
And as a matter of principle,
I won't pretend that I took it.

07:16.046 --> 07:17.399
They have an eyewitness.

07:17.399 --> 07:21.323
Look here, I might seem like
some court­appointed charity case,

07:21.323 --> 07:23.689
but I'm an honest man.
I don't steal.

07:23.689 --> 07:27.000
And I won't agree to any plea
that says otherwise.

07:27.211 --> 07:28.535
Mr Seymore.

07:28.914 --> 07:30.181
Hi, Sally Heep.

07:30.181 --> 07:31.502
I'm in litigation at the firm.

07:31.502 --> 07:32.705
I know that.

07:32.705 --> 07:36.334
–You in court today, or…
–No, but you are.

07:36.334 --> 07:39.252
I'm here to observe
your work, Ms Heep.

07:39.252 --> 07:40.658
Good luck.

07:49.266 --> 07:50.377
Denny,

07:51.329 --> 07:55.108
the lawyer who got the T.R.O.

07:55.737 --> 07:58.508
On the Kaneb construction project…

07:58.508 --> 08:00.525
Ah. 
Pay him out, Paul.

08:00.525 --> 08:01.941
Give him a bottle of scotch
and some money

08:01.941 --> 08:04.745
to buy some more bus bench ads.

08:04.745 --> 08:07.149
He says he's your son.

08:21.470 --> 08:23.518
It's true.

08:23.518 --> 08:26.206
You're a lawyer now.

08:26.692 --> 08:28.453
Hey…

08:28.705 --> 08:30.578
Dad.

08:38.586 --> 08:40.424
You got a needle in your head.

08:40.424 --> 08:43.386
Small accident.
Not to worry.

08:43.607 --> 08:45.573
Son.

08:46.133 --> 08:47.975
Dad.

08:59.240 --> 09:02.663
You're a lawyer now.
That's how you greet people?

09:03.479 --> 09:04.905
Donny Crane.

09:09.208 --> 09:10.635
Denny Crane.

09:10.907 --> 09:12.383
Donny Crane.

09:12.383 --> 09:13.339
